Hymn.Arabic: " الرب يعطى كلمة للمبشرين بقوة عظيمة،
Hymn.English: 11 The Lord gave the word; Great was the company of those who proclaimed it:.

Hymn.Arabic: عجيب هو الله في قديسيه، إله إسرائيل هو يعطى، قوة وعزاء لشعبه. هلليلويا "
Hymn.English: 35 O God, You are more awesome than Your holy places. The God of Israel is He who gives strength and power to His people.     Alleluia
